    <entry>
      <title>利用Spring实现QQ邮箱的发送</title>
      <link href="/posts/2258766305/"/>
      <url>/posts/2258766305/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="注册邮箱权限"><a href="#注册邮箱权限" class="headerlink" title="注册邮箱权限"></a>注册邮箱权限</h1><p>打开QQ邮箱点击顶部设置→账户<br>找到下面的这一模块开启POP3/SMTP服务（==注意：使用此功能的前提是不能开启QQ安全中心的邮箱保护，否则就会像我图片里面显示的一样，被锁定无法使用==）<br><strong>解锁方法：<br>下载手机版QQ安全中心，登录账号进行解锁</strong><br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200623092930330.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NTA5NzczMg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="邮箱设置页"><br>开启成功后我们会得到一段==授权码==，记得好好保存，Spring的配置中会使用到。</p><h1 id="进行Spring配置"><a href="#进行Spring配置" class="headerlink" title="进行Spring配置"></a>进行Spring配置</h1><h2 id="在pom文件中加入依赖"><a href="#在pom文件中加入依赖" class="headerlink" title="在pom文件中加入依赖"></a>在pom文件中加入依赖</h2><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 邮箱依赖 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-mail<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果使用的是idea编译器，记得右击pom.xml文件maven一下<br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200623094232427.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NTA5NzczMg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="配置完pom文件，进行maven"></p><h2 id="配置application-properties文件"><a href="#配置application-properties文件" class="headerlink" title="配置application.properties文件"></a>配置application.properties文件</h2><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#配置邮件消息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.host=smtp.qq.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#发送邮件者信箱（也就是你申请POP3/SMTP服务的QQ号）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.username=**********@qq.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#申请PO3/SMTP服务时，给我们的邮箱的授权码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.password=*************</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.default-encoding=UTF-8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.port=465</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.properties.mail.smtp.socketFactory.class=javax.net.ssl.SSLSocketFactory</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">spring.mail.properties.mail.debug=true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Spring代码的编写"><a href="#Spring代码的编写" class="headerlink" title="Spring代码的编写"></a>Spring代码的编写</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RestController</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">EmailController</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Autowired</span></span><br><span class="line">    JavaMailSender mailSender;<span class="comment">//注入QQ发送邮件的bean，这个是pom文件中的不需要额外写</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//定义发送的内容 我这里发送一张图片 需要html标签</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> String body=<span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2010847556,4286271682&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0.jpg&#x27; alt=&#x27;&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@GetMapping(&quot;/qqemail&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title">qqemail</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            MimeMessage mimeMessage = <span class="keyword">this</span>.mailSender.createMimeMessage();</span><br><span class="line">            MimeMessageHelper message = <span class="keyword">new</span> MimeMessageHelper(mimeMessage);</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            message.setFrom(<span class="string">&quot;**********@qq.com&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//设置授权了的qq邮箱</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            String qq=<span class="string">&quot;*******@qq.com&quot;</span>;<span class="comment">//补全收件人地址</span></span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            message.setTo(qq);<span class="comment">//设置收件人</span></span><br><span class="line">            message.setSubject(<span class="string">&quot;测试&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//设置标题</span></span><br><span class="line">            message.setText(body,<span class="keyword">true</span>);  <span class="comment">//第二个参数true表示使用HTML语言来编写邮件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//            FileSystemResource file = new FileSystemResource(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//            File file = new File(&quot;图片路径&quot;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//            helper.addAttachment(&quot;图片.jpg&quot;, file);//添加带附件的邮件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//            helper.addInline(&quot;picture&quot;,file);//添加带静态资源的邮件</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">this</span>.mailSender.send(mimeMessage);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;发送成功&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception ex) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ex.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;发送成功&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编写完启动后台，直接访问<a href="http://localhost:8080/qqemail%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF">http://localhost:8080/qqemail即可</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
